~ 2 Thessalonians 1 ~

|1|
Paul and Silvanus and Timothy to the church of Thessalonians
in God ^our^ Father and ^the^ Lord Jesus Christ:

|2|
Grace to you and peace from God ^our^ Father and ^the^ Lord Jesus Christ.

|3|
We ought to always give thanks to God concerning you, brothers, even as 
it is right; because ^it^ exceedingly grows ^your^ faith and multiples 
the love^every^ one of you ^has toward^ [literally ^one of each all of 
you to^] one another,

